OL,6,FA coroner has pledged a 'full and
OL,7,Ffrank investigation' into the death of
OL,8,Fa schizophrenic patient who died under
OL,9,Fthe care of Devon Partnership NHS
OL,10,FTrust.
OL,12,FWilliam Northcott died in a care home
OL,13,Fin Torquay in July 2021 and an inquest
OL,14,Finto his death is being held in Exeter
OL,15,Ffrom Monday 13 January.
OL,17,FThe 39-year-old was first prescribed
OL,18,Fthe antipsychotic drug Clozapine in
OL,19,F2006 and 2011, and restarted in 2012.
