OL,3,CSchizophrenic was regularly 'coughing
OL,4,Cuntil he was purple', inquest told
OL,6,FMr Northcott's sister, Kate Spall, has
OL,7,Ftold the inquest she never knew he was
OL,8,Fon such a potent drug until his death.
OL,10,FShe also described her brother as "a
OL,11,Fone off, incredibly bright and lucid".
OL,13,FMs Spall also said "it's very sad the
OL,14,Fworld will never get to know the
OL,15,FWilliam we knew".
OL,17,FShe said red flags were "explained
OL,18,Faway" - including weight gain,
OL,19,Ffatigue, and coughing until he was
OL,20,Fpurple in the face.
