OL,6,FAssistant Coroner Lousie Wiltshire has
OL,7,Fpromised a "full and frank
OL,8,Finvestigation" that will include the
OL,9,Finitial decision to prescribe
OL,10,FClozapine and how it was monitored in
OL,11,Fthe 12 months leading up to Mr
OL,12,FNorthcott's death.
OL,14,FThe inquest will also examine whether
OL,15,Fhe had raised levels of the drug in
OL,16,Fhis system and for how long.
OL,18,FIt will also look into his use of
OL,19,Famphetamine and how it may have
OL,20,Fcontributed to his death.
