OL,6,FMr Northcott had a history of
OL,7,Fsuffering poor mental health. He was
OL,8,Fadmitted to Devon Partnership Trust's
OL,9,FLangdon Hospital in November 2012 and
OL,10,Fwas discharged to a residential
OL,11,Ffacility in October 2014.
OL,13,FIn December 2018 William was
OL,14,Ftransferred to Georgian House where he
OL,15,Fwas receiving one-to-one, 24 hours a
OL,16,Fday support.
